Catalyst::Plugin::HTTP::MeetsConditions 0.001000
================================================

Support for HTTP/1.1 ETag and Last-Modified techniques.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Class::Accessor::Fast, HTTP::Headers::ETag, List::Util and NEXT.

Catalyst::Runtime, Test::WWW::Mechanize::Catalyst, Test::More and ok
for testing.

